paragraphs.title: Check for null values in all the columns
paragraphs.text:
%spark2.sql
SELECT 
    sum(case when cityname is null then 1 else 0 end) as cityname,
    sum(case when statename is null then 1 else 0 end) as statename,
    sum(case when latitude is null then 1 else 0 end) as latitude,
    sum(case when longitude is null then 1 else 0 end) as longitude,
    sum(case when year is null then 1 else 0 end) as year,
    sum(case when month is null then 1 else 0 end) as month,
    sum(case when day is null then 1 else 0 end) as day,
    sum(case when pollutionlevel is null then 1 else 0 end) as month,
    sum(case when aqilevel is null then 1 else 0 end) as aqilevel,
    sum(case when vulnerablepopulation is null then 1 else 0 end) as vulnerablepopulation,
    sum(case when hospitaladmissions is null then 1 else 0 end) as hospitaladmissions,
    sum(case when renewableenergysource is null then 1 else 0 end) as renewableenergysource,
    sum(case when particulatematter is null then 1 else 0 end) as particulatematter,
    sum(case when nitrogenoxides is null then 1 else 0 end) as nitrogenoxides,
    sum(case when sulfurdioxide is null then 1 else 0 end) as sulfurdioxide,
    sum(case when ozone is null then 1 else 0 end) as ozone,
    sum(case when carbonmonoxide is null then 1 else 0 end) as carbonmonoxide
from airpollution

paragraphs.title: Displays which state most uses renewable energy source
paragraphs.text:
%spark2.sql
select statename, count(renewableenergysource) from airpollutionView where renewableenergysource in ('Natural gas', 'Biomass', 'Geothermal', 'Nuclear power')
group by statename
order by count(renewableenergysource) desc

paragraphs.title: Displays state has max aqi level
paragraphs.text:
%spark2.sql
select statename, avg(aqilevel) from airpollutionView 
group by statename
order by avg(aqilevel) asc

paragraphs.title: Displays state has max pollution level
paragraphs.text:
%spark2.sql
select statename, avg(pollutionlevel) from airpollutionView 
group by statename
order by avg(pollutionlevel) asc
